---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About">
  <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>
  <div class="about-content">
    <p>
      Azadi Wire aggregates English-language news about Iran from multiple
      independent sources. Azadi means freedom in Farsi.
    </p>
    <p>
      Articles are automatically sorted into topics like human rights, politics,
      culture, protests, sanctions, and war. A daily digest summarizes the top
      stories so you can stay informed at a glance.
    </p>
    <p>
      You can search articles, bookmark stories for later, and subscribe via
      RSS to get updates in your reader of choice.
    </p>
    <p>
      This project is not affiliated with any government, political
      organization, or news outlet.
    </p>
    <p>
      Source available on <a href="https://github.com/alexraskin/azadi-wire" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>
